onel Smith ||\n|-\n| ''[[The Opponent (1988 film)|The Opponent]]'' || Victor ||\n|-\n| ''[[Spike of Bensonhurst]]'' || Baldo Cacetti || Nominated \u2013 [[Independent Spirit Award for Best Supporting Male]]\n|-\n| ''{{sortname|The|Big Turnaround|nolink=yes}}'' || Father Lopez ||\n|-\n| ''[[Moving Target (1988 Italian film)|Moving Target]]'' || Captain Morrison ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 1989 || ''[[Gummib\u00e4rchen k\u00fc\u00dft man nicht]]'' || Bischof ||\n|-\n| ''[[Laser Mission]]'' || Professor Braun ||\n|-\n| ''[[Jake Spanner, Private Eye]]'' || Sal Piccolo ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 1990 || ''[[Any Man's Death]]'' || Herr Gantz ||\n|-\n| ''[[Appearances (1990 film)|Appearances]]'' || Emil Danzig ||\n|-\n| ''Tides of War'' || Doctor ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1991 || ''{{sortname|The|Last Match|nolink=yes}}'' || Coach ||\n|-\n| ''Mountain of Diamonds'' || Ernie ||\n|-\n| 1992 || ''[[Mistress (1992 film)|Mistress]]'' || Himself || Cameo\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1993 || ''Tier\u00e4rztin Christine'' || Dr. Gustav Gruber ||\n|-\n| ''{{ill|Der blaue Diamant|de|3=Der blaue Diamant|lt=Hunt for the Blue Diamond}}''<!-- Originally ''Der blaue Diamant'' --> || Hans Kroger ||\n|-\n| 1994 || ''[[Outlaws: The Legend of O.B. Taggart]]'' || Sheriff Laughton ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1995 || ''Tier\u00e4rztin Christine II: The Temptation'' || Dr. Gustav Gruber ||\n|-\n| ''Captiva Island'' || Arty ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 1996 || ''[[The Wild Bunch: An Album in Montage]]'' || Himself || Voice; Documentary\n|-\n| ''[[All Dogs Go to Heaven 2]]'' || Carface Carruthers || Voice\n|-\n| ''[[Merlin's Shop of Mystical Wonders]]'' || Grandfather ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 1997 || ''[[Ernest Borgnine on the Bus]]'' || Himself || Documentary\n|-\n| ''[[McHale's Navy (1997 film)|McHale's Navy]]'' || Admiral Quinton McHale, Sr. (a.k.a. Cobra) || Based on the series [[McHale's Navy|of the same name]]\n|-\n| ''[[Gattaca]]'' || Caesar ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" | 1998 || ''[[Small Soldiers]]'' || Ki